---
import { otherprojects } from "../../data/otherprojects.json";
---

<section class="bg-primary">
    <div class="px-8 2xl:max-w-7xl mx-auto py-6">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-4 text-secondary gap-6">
            <p
                class="text-base lg:col-start-2 leading-relaxed"
                data-aos="fade-up"
                data-aos-duration="2000"
            >
                Tim Porter is a managing director of SC Capital Partners, a full
                time business financial consulting firm.
            </p>
            <p
                class="text-base lg:col-start-2 leading-relaxed underline underline-offset-4"
                data-aos="fade-up"
                data-aos-duration="2500"
            >
                We are currently available for inquiries. If you need assistance
                with a business or finance issue, do not hesitate to get in
                contact. <a href="mailto:tim@timporter.associates"
                    >tim@timporter.associates
                </a>
            </p>
            <p
                class="text-base lg:col-start-4 leading-relaxed"
                data-aos="fade-up"
                data-aos-duration="2500"
            >
                With over 50 years of experience, I have the knowledge,
                experience, and expertise to help you navigate the complexities
                of the financial world. I am dedicated to providing the highest
                level of service to my clients, and I am committed to helping
                them acheive their financial goals.
            </p>
            <p
                class="text-base lg:col-start-4 leading-relaxed"
                data-aos="fade-up"
                data-aos-duration="3000"
            >
                I specialize in assisting organizations in the development of
                their financial infrastructures, optimizing their business
                models, and obtaining the growth capital needed to support their
                businesses.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
